---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Apps by Curated Design – Curated Design Studio
description: Digital tools and app support pages by Curated Design Studio.
permalink: apps/index.html
htmlClass: app-page
bodyClass: app-page min-h-screen font-inter
sectionTop: true
---
<main class="page-main">
    {% include "partials/hero-brand.njk" %}

    <section class="app-content">
        <div class="app-wrap">
            <header class="app-header">
                <p class="app-kicker">Digital Tools</p>
                <h1 class="app-title">Apps by Curated Design</h1>
                <p class="app-lead">
                    A small collection of practical tools developed alongside the studio. They sit quietly here for support, privacy, and App Store reference.
                </p>
            </header>

            <div class="app-card-grid" aria-label="Apps">
                {% for app in apps.items %}
                <a class="app-card" href="/apps/{{ app.slug }}/">
                    <p class="app-card-kicker">{{ app.eyebrow }}</p>
                    <h2>{{ app.name }}</h2>
                    <p>{{ app.description }}</p>
                    <span class="app-card-link">View details</span>
                </a>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

            <p class="app-small-note">
                The main studio remains focused on interiors, procurement, and design work. These pages provide public app information and support links.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
